title: Oracle Devservice not working

labels.name: area/jdbc
labels.description: Issues related to the JDBC extensions

body:

### Expected behavior

### How to Reproduce?

Steps to reproduce:

1. Generate new Quarkus application using code.quarkus.io
2. Add `quarkus-jdbc-oracle` and `quarkus-hibernate-orm-panache` extension
3. Run `quarkus dev`
